name: Iranon style TI
description:
Style embedding trained on Iranon's art. Very good for generating busty women with thick lips. I recommend to use UnstableInkDream model for this embedding, when I tested it on Anything V4.5 results were significantly worse (looks like UnstableInkDream is good for non-anime cartoony styles in general). https://civitai.com/models/1540/unstableinkdream

P.S. it was trained on highly nsfw art, so put nsfw words into negative prompt if you don't want to accidentally create nsfw generations
